OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,FThe University of Sussex has been
OL,7,Ffined #585,000 after an investigation
OL,8,Ffound it had failed to uphold freedom
OL,9,Fof speech.
OL,11,FThe investigation by the Office for
OL,12,FStudents (OfS) found documents which
OL,13,Fgovern university policy also failed
OL,14,Fto safeguard academic freedom, as well
OL,15,Fas finding failings in the management
OL,16,Fand governance of the university.
