OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,FIt was launched following protests
OL,7,Fcalling for the dismissal of senior
OL,8,Facademic Professor Kathleen Stock in
OL,9,F2021 after she was accused of
OL,10,Ftransphobia.
OL,12,FProfessor Stock faced protests on the
OL,13,Fcampus after publishing a book on
OL,14,Fgender identity, an experience she
OL,15,Ftold the BBC was like a "surreal
OL,16,Fanxiety dream". She resigned her
OL,17,Fposition at the university in 2021.
