OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,FThe university's vice-chancellor,
OL,7,FProfessor Sasha Roseneil, said the
OL,8,Funiversity would legally challenge the
OL,9,FOfS's findings.
OL,11,FThe OfS report found no evidence
OL,12,FProfessor Stock said anything unlawful
OL,13,Fduring her time at the university and
OL,14,Fconcluded its "Trans and Non-Binary
OL,15,FEquality Policy Statement failed to
OL,16,Fuphold the freedom of speech and
OL,17,Facademic freedom public interest
OL,18,Fgovernance principles" required by the
OL,19,Fwatchdog.
