OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,FIt also found the university did not
OL,7,Fhave "adequate and effective
OL,8,Fmanagement and governance
OL,9,Farrangements" in place and that the
OL,10,Fshortcomings led to a "chilling
OL,11,Feffect" with staff and students
OL,12,Fpotentially self-censoring certain
OL,13,Fviews.
