OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,FArif Ahmed, director for freedom of
OL,7,Fspeech and academic freedom at the
OL,8,FOfS, said: "Free speech is a
OL,9,Ffundamentally important aspect of our
OL,10,Fsuccessful and vibrant higher
OL,11,Feducation sector. All universities and
OL,12,Fcolleges have a duty to protect
OL,13,Facademic freedom and to take steps to
OL,14,Fsecure freedom of speech within the
OL,15,Flaw.
