OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,F"The OfS's findings mean that it is
OL,7,Fnow virtually impossible for
OL,8,Funiversities to prevent abuse,
OL,9,Fharassment or bullying on our
OL,10,Fcampuses," she said. "It means
OL,11,Funiversities cannot protect groups
OL,12,Fsubject to harmful propaganda or
OL,13,Fdetermine that stereotyped assumptions
OL,14,Fshould not be relied upon in the
OL,15,Funiversity curriculum.
OL,17,F"The OfS is effectively decreeing
OL,18,Flibertarian free speech absolutism as
OL,19,Fthe fundamental principle for UK
OL,20,Funiversities. In our view, the OfS is
OL,21,Fperpetuating the culture wars."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]rD@VOUyD@AOU}D@_O]
