OL,6,FShe criticised the way the three-and-a-
OL,7,Fhalf year investigation was conducted,
OL,8,Fsaying nobody employed by the
OL,9,Funiversity was interviewed.
OL,11,F"The circumstances around Professor
OL,12,FStock's departure from the University
OL,13,Fof Sussex are deeply regrettable," she
OL,14,Fsaid. "Sussex has consistently and
OL,15,Fpublicly defended her right to pursue
OL,16,Fher academic work and to express her
OL,17,Fgender critical beliefs.
