OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,F"Academic freedom and freedom of
OL,7,Fspeech are the foundational elements
OL,8,Fof a university, and the university is
OL,9,Fcommitted to ensuring that diversity
OL,10,Fin all its forms, particularly
OL,11,Fdiversity of thought and identity, are
OL,12,Fable to flourish at Sussex."
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,15,Fsaid free speech and academic freedom
OL,16,Fwere "non-negotiables" in universities
OL,17,Fand "robust action will be taken" if
OL,18,Fthey are not upheld.
