OL,3,CUniversity fined #585,000 following
OL,4,Cfree speech investigation
OL,6,F"If you go to university you must be
OL,7,Fprepared to have your views
OL,8,Fchallenged, hear contrary opinions and
OL,9,Fbe exposed to uncomfortable truths,"
OL,10,Fshe said. "We are giving the OfS
OL,11,Fstronger powers on freedom of speech
OL,12,Fso students and academics are not
OL,13,Fmuzzled by the chilling effect
OL,14,Fdemonstrated in this case.
OL,16,F"Through our Plan for Change we will
OL,17,Frestore the integrity of our
OL,18,Funiversities as rigorous centres of
OL,19,Fintellectual debate, sparking new
OL,20,Fideas that will cement their status as
OL,21,Fengines of growth and opportunity."
